## ‚ö†Ô∏è Lessons Learned

- Augmentation must follow complete preprocessing (ICA, filtering, etc.)
- Never apply augmentation to validation/test sets ‚Äî it leads to data leakage
- Not all augmentations are beneficial: poorly matched noise or excessive shifts can distort diagnostic features

